---
layout: default
meta_title: Home
meta_description: Daily meals delivered to NHS hospital staff
body_class: home
title: Meals for the NHS
---
<main id="main" class="main flex flex-1 h-full flex-col focus:outline-none" tabindex="-1">
    <div class="absolute l-0 r-0 h-16 md:h-32 lg:h-48 w-full bg-blue-800"></div>
    <div class="relative">
        <div class="container flex items-center md:w-4/5 mx-auto justify-center text-center px-4 md:pt-4 md:pb-16">
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/3 p-2">
                <div class="rounded bg-top md:bg-center bg-cover bg-no-repeat pb-half md:pb-twothirds w-full shadow-2xl" style="background-image: url('/images/photos/order-1.jpg')"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="hidden md:block w-1/3 p-2">
                <div class="rounded bg-center bg-cover bg-no-repeat pb-square w-full shadow-2xl" style="background-image: url('/images/photos/order-2.jpg')"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="hidden md:block w-1/3 p-2">
                <div class="rounded bg-center bg-cover bg-no-repeat pb-twothirds w-full shadow-2xl" style="background-image: url('/images/photos/order-3.jpg')"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container md:w-4/5 lg:w-3/4 xl:w-3/5 mx-auto text-center px-4 pt-4 py-6 md:pb-16 lg:pb-24">
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl pb-3 md:pb-6">Help buy meals for the NHS staff fighting COVID-19</h1>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-2xl text-gray-700 pb-4">After 18-hour shifts trying to save our lives from COVID-19, NHS Hospital Staff are faced with canteens that shut at 5pm.</p>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-2xl text-gray-800 pb-2 font-bold">Help get food to wards, today.</p>
        <div class="mx-auto pt-3 flex justify-center">
            <script src="https://donorbox.org/widget.js" paypalExpress="false"></script><iframe frameborder="0" height="93px" name="donorbox" scrolling="no" seamless="seamless" src="https://donorbox.org/embed/meals-for-the-nhs-frontline-heroes?only_donation_meter=true&donation_meter_color=%232c5282" style="max-width:425px; min-width:310px; max-height:none!important" width="100%"></iframe>
        </div>
        {% include "components/donation_buttons.njk" %}
    </div>
    {% include "components/problem.njk" %}
    {% include "components/endorsements.njk" %}
    {% include "components/tweets.njk" %}
    {% include "components/donation_button.njk" %}
    {% include "components/team.njk" %}
    {% include "components/donation_form.njk" %}
    <div class="">
        <div class="container md:w-4/5 mx-auto justify-center text-center px-4 py-6 md:py-16">
            <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 lg:mb-12">Hospitals we're hoping to feed</h3>
            <ul class="flex flex-wrap justify-center">
                {%- for hospital in collections.hospital -%}
                    <li class="py-2 px-1">
                        <a href="{{ hospital.url }}" class="rounded p-2 bg-blue-100 hover:bg-blue-300">{{ hospital.data.name }}</a>
                    </li>
                {%- endfor -%}
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>
<div class="pb-8 mx-auto">
    {% include "components/donation_buttons.njk" %}
    {% include "components/social-share.njk" %}
</div>

<script src="https://donorbox.org/widget.js" paypalExpress="false"></script>
